\begin_body

\begin_layout Section*
Case - View the current booking information
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Use case: View the current booking information
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Level: User goal
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Primary actor: Staff who is currently using the system
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Scope: Display the current booking information for the current system user.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Stakeholders:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Staff: Wants to view his current booking records, total number of bookings
 and the maximum booking count.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Preconditions:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
The staff should be an authorized user (logged-in).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Success Guarantee:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
The system will provide the total number of bookings of the current staff.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system will list out the current booking records including the booking
 booking reference number, the booking date & time, room number and room
 location for the staff.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Main Success Scenario:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
After the successful 
\color red
authentication and authorization process
\color inherit
, the system will display the 
\color red
current user information
\color inherit
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The 
\color red
system
\color inherit
 will show the 
\color red
total number of bookings of the current staff
\color inherit
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The 
\color red
system
\color inherit
 will list out the 
\color red
current booking records
\color inherit
 including the 
\color red
booking reference number
\color inherit
, the 
\color red
booking date & time
\color inherit
, 
\color red
room number
\color inherit
 and 
\color red
room location
\color inherit
 for the 
\color red
staff
\color inherit
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
This system will update automatically if the 
\color red
booking record
\color inherit
 changes (i.e.
 
\color red
new booking
\color inherit
 has been made).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Extensions:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
If the booking record displayed is not incorrect
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Multiple reasons could cause this to happen.
 Such as an emergency maintenance occurred in the booked room and other
 administrative reasons.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Technical problems such as IO Errors could also cause the problem.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The staff should contact the system administration staff for further enquiry.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
